  m_text: "You've just tossed your graduation cap in the air \u2014 and watched your
    bank account hit zero on the way down. A degree in hand, a mountain of living
    expenses ahead, and zero job offers on the horizon. Your confidence is shaky,
    your skills are still rough around the edges, and the clock is already ticking.\nIt's
    time to open your laptop, start grinding those job boards, and claw your way
    to financial freedom.\n<b>How to Play</b>: Click app icons to open them, click
    buttons to interact, and navigate the desktop just like a real computer. Your
    mouse is your only tool \u2014 use it wisely."
